msgstr "您无法在 CPU 上运行端到端测试。"

msgid "=== \"Single-card\""
msgstr "=== \"单卡\""

msgid "=== \"Multi-card\""
msgstr "=== \"多卡\""

msgid ""
"For running nightly single-node model test cases locally, refer to the "
"following example."
msgstr "如需在本地运行夜间单节点模型测试用例，请参考以下示例。"

msgid ""
"For running nightly multi-node model test cases locally, refer to the "
"`Running Locally` section in [Multi Node Test](./multi_node_test.md)."
msgstr "如需在本地运行夜间多节点模型测试用例，请参考[多节点测试](./multi_node_test.md)中的“本地运行”部分。"

msgid "#### E2E test examples"
msgstr "#### 端到端测试示例"

msgid ""
"- Offline test example: [`tests/e2e/pull_request/one_card/test_camem.py`](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/tests/e2e/pull_request/one_card/test_camem.py)\n"
"- Online test example: [`tests/e2e/pull_request/two_card/aclgraph/test_single_request_aclgraph.py`](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/tests/e2e/pull_request/two_card/aclgraph/test_single_request_aclgraph.py)\n"
"- Correctness test example: [`tests/e2e/pull_request/one_card/aclgraph/test_aclgraph_accuracy.py`](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/tests/e2e/pull_request/one_card/aclgraph/test_aclgraph_accuracy.py)"
msgstr ""
"- 离线测试示例：[`tests/e2e/pull_request/one_card/test_camem.py`](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/tests/e2e/pull_request/one_card/test_camem.py)\n"
"- 在线测试示例：[`tests/e2e/pull_request/two_card/aclgraph/test_single_request_aclgraph.py`](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/tests/e2e/pull_request/two_card/aclgraph/test_single_request_aclgraph.py)\n"
"- 正确性测试示例：[`tests/e2e/pull_request/one_card/aclgraph/test_aclgraph_accuracy.py`](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/tests/e2e/pull_request/one_card/aclgraph/test_aclgraph_accuracy.py)"

msgid ""
"The CI resource is limited, and you might need to reduce the number of "
"layers of a model. Below is an example of how to generate a reduced layer "
"model:"
msgstr "CI 资源有限，您可能需要减少模型的层数。以下是如何生成精简层模型的示例："

msgid ""
"1. Fork the original model repo in modelscope. All the files in the repo except for weights are required.\n"
"2. Set `num_hidden_layers` to the expected number of layers, e.g., `{\"num_hidden_layers\": 2,}`\n"
"3. Copy the following python script as `generate_random_weight.py`. Set the relevant parameters `MODEL_LOCAL_PATH`, `DIST_DTYPE` and `DIST_MODEL_PATH` as needed:"
msgstr ""
"1. 在 modelscope 中 fork 原始模型仓库。需要仓库中除权重外的所有文件。\n"
"2. 将 `num_hidden_layers` 设置为期望的层数，例如 `{\"num_hidden_layers\": 2,}`\n"
"3. 复制以下 Python 脚本并命名为 `generate_random_weight.py`。根据需要设置相关参数 `MODEL_LOCAL_PATH`、`DIST_DTYPE` 和 `DIST_MODEL_PATH`："

msgid "### Run doctest"
msgstr "### 运行 doctest"

msgid ""
"vllm-ascend provides a `vllm-ascend/tests/e2e/run_doctests.sh` command to run all doctests in the doc files.\n"
"The doctest is a good way to make sure docs stay current and examples remain executable, which can be run locally as follows:"
msgstr ""
"vllm-ascend 提供了一个 `vllm-ascend/tests/e2e/run_doctests.sh` 命令来运行文档文件中的所有 doctest。\n"
"doctest 是确保文档保持最新且示例保持可执行性的好方法，可以按如下方式在本地运行："

msgid ""
"This will reproduce the same environment as the CI. See "
"[labeled_doctest.yaml](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/.github/workflows/labeled_doctest.yaml)."
msgstr ""
"这将重现与 CI 相同的环境。请参阅 [labeled_doctest.yaml](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/.github/workflows/labeled_doctest.yaml)。"

